text: Jolanta Studzienna (born 2 January 1977) is a Polish volleyball player and volleyball coach. She won a gold medal at the 2009/10 Polish championships. She played for Skra Warszawa, Panathinaikos, OMS Senica, Bank Pocztowy Pałac Bydgoszcz, BKS Stal Bielsko-Biała, DPD Legionovia Legionowo. She coached for Siódemkę SK Bank Legionovia. == References == Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Polish volleyball players Category:Volleyball coaches
